Logger.Levels - io.github.ettoolset.tools.logger中的Enum Class
The levels contain Levels.INFO, Levels.DEBUG and Levels.SEVERE
For Levels.INFO, you can call: info(), error(), fatal()
For Levels.DEBUG, you can call: info(), error(), fatal(), debug(), severe(), fine()
For Levels.SEVERE, you can call: info(), error(), fatal(), severe(), fine()
If you call the functions that does not match the level you have declared, a LevelNotMatchException will be thrown

RunMethod - io.github.ettoolset.tools.deamon中的Enum Class
RunMethod declares the method that you may use in a deamon process
The methods contains RunMethod.GUI and RunMethod.CONSOLE
For RunMethod.GUI, the output of deamon info will be shown in a window
For RunMethod.CONSOLE, the output will be printed as log (in this project)
